longBusinessDescription:
Buska is the Online Presence Monitoring tool for startups, SMBs and Entrepreneurs. 
We track every mention of your brand (or competitors) online:
from social media (Facebook, Linkedin, X, Youtube, Tiktok, Instagram...),
from communities (like Reddit or Product Hunt)
from the Web (Sites, Articles, Blogs, etc) 
Receive notifications in real time every time your company name is cited.
So you can stay ahead of the curve and answer any comment or feedback. 
Get the pulse of your brand, with our Sentiment Analysis to monitor your Online Reputation at a glance.

businessDescription:
Hopfab is your privileged partner and allows you to benefit from our network of nearly 350 certified French craftsmen to carry out your layout projects, furniture, custom-made lighting, planting and signage ...

Hopfab brings you:
* access to the best craftsmen and know-how positioned on all price ranges,
* a precise selection of workshops to meet the specificities of each project (deadlines, budget, know-how, location, etc.);
* a secure platform for contracting and a proven project management methodology for more than 800 projects in 3 years;
* a team of experts to support you in the relationship with your craftsman.
